WEBVTT

00:00.801 --> 00:03.637
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:33.401 --> 00:35.403
[ HIP-HOP MUSIC PLAYING ]

00:35.403 --> 00:37.105
IT'S A SHAME
TO BREAK THIS UP.

00:37.105 --> 00:39.107
I FEEL LIKE THE FATHER
IN "FOOTLOOSE."

00:39.107 --> 00:40.708
THE REMAKE
OR THE ORIGINAL?

00:40.708 --> 00:43.010
HOW OLD ARE YOU, MAN?

00:43.010 --> 00:45.646
[ MUSIC CONTINUES ]

00:56.224 --> 00:57.725
[ MUSIC STOPS,
INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

00:57.725 --> 01:00.128
SORRY, BUT YOU GUYS
HAVE ALL GOT TO GO!

01:00.128 --> 01:01.662
THE OWNER
DOESN'T WANT YOU HERE!

01:01.662 --> 01:03.864
THE OWNER WANTS YOU GONE.
I WANT YOU GONE. LET'S GO.

01:03.864 --> 01:05.533
DUDE,
WE WAS JUST DANCING.

01:05.533 --> 01:07.468
OH, WELL, YOU KNOW, HONEY,
DANCE YOUR ASS BACK HOME.

01:07.468 --> 01:08.802
IT'S TIME
TO CLEAR OUT, OKAY?

01:08.802 --> 01:10.338
COME ON. CLEAR OUT.
EVERYBODY OUT. OUT.

01:10.338 --> 01:12.440
LET'S GO.
ARE YOU GONNA
MAKE US GO AWAY?

01:12.440 --> 01:13.874
HEY.
WE AIN'T DOING NOTHING.

01:13.874 --> 01:15.609
GET OUT OF MY FACE.
I'M GONNA HAVE TO ARREST YOU.

01:15.609 --> 01:17.378
LET'S GO.
HEY, HEY, WHOA!

01:17.378 --> 01:19.380
FOR DOING WHAT?
YOU CAN'T PUT YOUR HANDS
ON A COP.

01:19.380 --> 01:23.151
WHOA! WHOA! WHOA! WHOA!
YOUR PARENTS ARE GONNA HAVE TO
BAIL YOU OUT OF JAIL.

01:23.151 --> 01:24.585
Woman:
GET YOUR HANDS OFF OF HER!

01:24.585 --> 01:26.254
GET OFF! NO!
WHOA! WHOA! WHOA!

01:26.254 --> 01:28.322
I'M NOT! COME ON!
LET US JUST DANCE!
Sammy: PARTNER!

01:28.322 --> 01:29.490
GET BACK. GET BACK.

01:29.490 --> 01:31.091
WE AIN'T EVEN
DOING NOTHING.

01:31.091 --> 01:32.092
MISS. MISS.

01:32.092 --> 01:33.261
HEY! WHOA!

01:33.261 --> 01:34.928
WHOA!
YEAH!
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

01:34.928 --> 01:36.096
BACK UP! GET BACK!

01:36.096 --> 01:37.998
WHOA!
[ SPITS ]

01:37.998 --> 01:41.001
COPS ROUTINELY
FIND THEMSELVES UNDERWATER.

01:41.001 --> 01:44.772
THE BEST MANAGE TO KEEP
THEIR HEADS ABOVE THE SURFACE,

01:44.772 --> 01:48.209
BUT EVEN FOR A STRONG SWIMMER
LIKE OFFICER BEN SHERMAN,

01:48.209 --> 01:51.545
THE UNDERTOW CAN BE TRICKY.

01:56.049 --> 01:58.619
[ UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYING ]

02:03.991 --> 02:05.526
[ SIGHS ]

02:05.526 --> 02:07.928
SO, IT'S LIKE THIS
EVERY WEEKEND?

02:07.928 --> 02:09.029
PRETTY MUCH.

02:09.029 --> 02:10.664
THE MAN'S
STILL HOLDING ON

02:10.664 --> 02:13.066
TO THAT SILVER LAKE
SHIT, SAMMY.

02:13.066 --> 02:14.502
YOU NEED TO SCHOOL HIM.

02:14.502 --> 02:16.003
[ Chuckling ] MAN LIKES
LIVING IN A SHOE BOX.

02:16.003 --> 02:17.338
WHAT CAN I TELL YOU?

02:17.338 --> 02:18.739
HEY, I LIVE 15 MINUTES
FROM THE DIVISION.

02:18.739 --> 02:19.840
YOU GUYS LIVE TWO HOURS.

02:19.840 --> 02:22.109
I DON'T NEED TO LIVE
IN CASTAIC COPLAND

02:22.109 --> 02:23.344
FOR PERSONAL VALIDATION.

02:23.344 --> 02:25.579
COPS NEED THE LONG DRIVE
TO DECOMPRESS.

02:25.579 --> 02:30.284
COME HOME TO A HOUSE,
YARD, DOG, A HOUSEBOAT.

02:30.284 --> 02:31.552
A LIFE.

02:31.552 --> 02:32.486
YEAH.

02:32.486 --> 02:34.688
I GOT BETTER WAYS
OF DECOMPRESSING.

02:34.688 --> 02:36.123
HI.

02:36.123 --> 02:37.891
HEY.

02:39.860 --> 02:41.161
MMM-MMM!

02:41.161 --> 02:44.031
OFFICER, I'M IN NEED
OF SOME ASSISTANCE.

02:44.031 --> 02:45.399
OH, SHOW ME HANDLING.

02:45.399 --> 02:47.601
GOD, I HOPE SO.
[ LAUGHS ]

02:50.571 --> 02:52.440
SEE, NOW,
THE AVERAGE BROTHER

02:52.440 --> 02:54.007
WOULD SETTLE FOR SOME...

02:54.007 --> 02:56.176
"UGLY BETTY" TYPE CHICK.

02:56.176 --> 03:00.147
WHITE BOYS GO BEYONCГ©
ALL THE WAY.

03:00.147 --> 03:02.283
OH!

03:04.485 --> 03:06.920
SPIKE LEE
HAD IT RIGHT, MAN.

03:06.920 --> 03:08.689
[ SHRIEKS ]

03:08.689 --> 03:10.891
Tang:
HEY, HOW'S IT GOING?

03:10.891 --> 03:12.893
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

03:14.328 --> 03:15.696
[ SIGHS ]

03:15.696 --> 03:19.199
POROSUS CROCODILE BAG.
IT'S WORTH LIKE $50,000.

03:19.199 --> 03:20.934
FOR A PURSE?
YEAH.

03:20.934 --> 03:22.370
COME ON.

03:22.370 --> 03:25.105
MY SISTER WOULD GIVE
HER LEFT ARM FOR THAT BAG.

03:25.105 --> 03:27.641
LOOKS LIKE
SOMEBODY ALREADY DID.

03:35.649 --> 03:36.684
NO BODY.

03:36.684 --> 03:38.519
MAYBE SHE MADE IT
TO THE HOSPITAL.

03:38.519 --> 03:40.254
MNH-MNH.
SEE -- NO SKID MARKS.

03:40.254 --> 03:41.389
WHOEVER HIT THIS LADY,

03:41.389 --> 03:42.990
THEY DIDN'T EVEN STOP.

03:42.990 --> 03:45.859
YOU DID CALL TRAFFIC ABOUT
THE STOPLIGHT CAMERAS, RIGHT?

03:45.859 --> 03:47.261
YES.

03:48.962 --> 03:50.531
WHAT'S NEW IN THE ZOO?

03:50.531 --> 03:52.566
Tang: TWO GUYS FROM THAT BAR
SAID THEY SAW

03:52.566 --> 03:54.535
A SILVER S.U.V.
SPEEDING DOWN THE BLOCK.

03:54.535 --> 03:56.069
ANOTHER SAID
IT WAS A SUBURBAN,

03:56.069 --> 03:58.939
AND SOME OTHER GUY SAID IT WAS
A FORD ESCAPE, NO PLATES.

03:58.939 --> 04:00.040
THAT'S A NICE BAG.

04:00.040 --> 04:01.375
YOU GUYS TAKE A LOOK?

04:01.375 --> 04:04.244
John: I FELT WITH SUCH
A DISTINGUISHED ACCESSORY,

04:04.244 --> 04:06.046
IT REQUIRED
A MORE DELICATE TOUCH.

04:06.046 --> 04:08.716
'COURSE YOU THOUGHT THAT.

04:08.716 --> 04:10.884
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:18.191 --> 04:21.094
MRS. MEREDITH WILLIAMS.

04:21.094 --> 04:23.531
ADDRESS IS OFF SUNSET.

04:23.531 --> 04:24.832
PROBABLY BEL AIR.

04:24.832 --> 04:26.634
CAN YOU GUYS HANDLE
THE NOTIFICATION?

04:26.634 --> 04:28.536
'CAUSE THIS SCAVENGER HUNT
FOR BODY PARTS

04:28.536 --> 04:30.137
IS GONNA TAKE
A WHILE.

04:30.137 --> 04:31.339
YEAH. SURE.

04:41.582 --> 04:43.651
Rucker:
I'M OLD-SCHOOL ALL THE WAY.

04:43.651 --> 04:46.119
DON'T START NONE.
WON'T BE NONE.

04:46.119 --> 04:47.688
YOU HAVE A QUESTION,
ANAWALT?

04:47.688 --> 04:50.324
WHY ARE YOU HANDING OUT
McDONALD'S APPLICATIONS?

04:50.324 --> 04:51.792
EVERY TIME
YOU FUCK UP,

04:51.792 --> 04:53.761
YOU'RE GONNA FILL OUT
ANOTHER LINE.

04:53.761 --> 04:57.398
AS YOUR NEW CAPTAIN,
LET ME MAKE IT CLEAR --

04:57.398 --> 05:00.668
WIPE YOUR FEET
BEFORE YOU STEP IN MY HOUSE.

05:00.668 --> 05:04.304
WE'RE GONNA SEND THE STREET
A MESSAGE.

05:04.304 --> 05:05.773
DROP THE LATTES

05:05.773 --> 05:08.942
AND GET YOUR NARROW BEHINDS
OUT OF YOUR PATROL CARS.

05:08.942 --> 05:12.245
WALK THE COURTYARDS,
THE ALLEYS, THE STREETS.

05:12.245 --> 05:14.782
SQUEEZE YOUR SNITCHES.

05:14.782 --> 05:18.452
YOU WANT OMELETTES,
YOU GOT TO CRACK EGGS.

05:18.452 --> 05:22.690
WE WILL BE
THE MOST PROACTIVE PATROL

05:22.690 --> 05:25.025
IN THE ENTIRE CITY.

05:25.025 --> 05:27.160
WE PROTECT.

05:27.160 --> 05:28.962
WE SERVE.

05:28.962 --> 05:31.999
AND WE KICK ASS
TILL WE SMELL SHIT.

05:31.999 --> 05:36.470
IF ANYBODY
HAS A PROBLEM WITH THAT,

05:36.470 --> 05:39.473
MICKEY D's NEEDS
ALL THE HELP THEY CAN GET.

05:39.473 --> 05:42.743
THE McRIB IS BACK.

05:50.017 --> 05:51.952
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

05:54.488 --> 05:55.689
HELLO.

05:55.689 --> 05:57.858
HI, SWEETIE.
IS YOUR MOTHER HOME?

05:57.858 --> 05:58.826
WHO ARE YOU?

05:58.826 --> 06:00.928
I NEED TO SPEAK
WITH YOUR MOTHER.

06:00.928 --> 06:02.463
MOM!

06:02.930 --> 06:04.598
Woman:
HONEY, WHAT DID I TELL YOU

06:04.598 --> 06:07.034
ABOUT ANSWERING THE DOOR
WHEN I'M NOT AROUND, ALL RIGHT?

06:07.034 --> 06:08.235
MAY I HELP YOU?

06:08.235 --> 06:09.670
YEAH.
I'M DETECTIVE ADAMS.

06:09.670 --> 06:12.039
THIS IS MY PARTNER,
DETECTIVE ROBINSON.

06:12.039 --> 06:14.875
DO YOU HAVE
A SILVER FORD ESCAPE?

06:14.875 --> 06:16.143
UH, YEAH.

06:48.141 --> 06:50.077
UGH.

06:52.446 --> 06:54.882
WE WERE GONNA LOSE
THE HOUSE.

06:54.882 --> 06:59.286
I JUST GOT A JOB, SO I DRANK
WITH A FEW OF MY BUDDIES.

06:59.286 --> 07:01.855
I THOUGHT I HIT
A COYOTE.

07:01.855 --> 07:05.158
YOU RIPPED A WOMAN IN HALF,
MR. DAVIS.

07:05.158 --> 07:07.761
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

07:11.599 --> 07:13.601
[ CRYING ]

07:13.601 --> 07:17.070
CONGRATULATIONS ON HIS NEW JOB
MAKING LICENSE PLATES.

07:17.070 --> 07:18.939
[ Chuckling ]
OOH, THAT'S HARSH.

07:18.939 --> 07:21.609
THEY'RE GONNA BE SCRAPING
CHUNKS OF MS. WILLIAMS

07:21.609 --> 07:23.744
OUT FROM UNDER THAT CAR
FOR HOURS.

07:25.412 --> 07:27.047
WE SHOULD MAKE HIM HELP.

07:28.616 --> 07:30.884
Ben: YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THIS NEW CAPTAIN?

07:30.884 --> 07:33.253
RUCKER WAS MY SARGE
WHEN I WORKED CRASH.

07:33.253 --> 07:34.454
YEAH? GOOD GUY?

07:34.454 --> 07:36.056
HE'S AN O.G.
WITH STRIPES ON HIS ARM

07:36.056 --> 07:37.658
AND THE ATTITUDE
TO MATCH.

07:37.658 --> 07:39.092
OUR JOB JUST GOT HARDER.

07:39.092 --> 07:40.060
HEY, JONES.

07:40.060 --> 07:42.863
ROOKIE BLUE
LOOKS NERVOUS.

07:42.863 --> 07:45.666
OH, SKIP IT, SHERMAN.
I'M A P2, JUST LIKE YOU.

07:45.666 --> 07:47.501
OH, I SERIOUSLY
DOUBT THAT.

07:47.501 --> 07:49.537
WHERE DID YOU
DO YOUR PROBATION?

07:49.537 --> 07:51.471
PACIFIC PALISADES?

07:51.471 --> 07:54.842
HEY, LOOK SHARP.
ACT SHARP. BE SHARP.

07:54.842 --> 07:56.577
AND, UH,
TRY NOT TO GET US KILLED.

07:56.577 --> 07:58.612
[ CAR DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

07:58.612 --> 08:00.648
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

08:01.849 --> 08:03.150
HEY, WOULDN'T IT
BE EASIER

08:03.150 --> 08:05.085
TO JUST ASK HER
FOR HER PHONE NUMBER?

08:05.085 --> 08:08.155
NOT NEARLY AS MUCH FUN.

08:08.155 --> 08:09.890
[ LAUGHS ]

08:11.391 --> 08:14.528
$10 MILLION HOUSE
TO GO WITH THE $50,000 HANDBAG.

08:14.528 --> 08:16.496
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
THAT MUCH?

08:16.496 --> 08:18.699
IN THIS ZIP CODE?
HELL, YES.

08:18.699 --> 08:22.169
MARY PICKFORD
USED TO LIVE HERE.

08:22.169 --> 08:23.771
WHO'S THAT?

08:23.771 --> 08:25.639
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

08:26.907 --> 08:30.210
WHAT, IS SHE AN EX-GIRLFRIEND
OF YOURS OR SOMETHING?

08:30.210 --> 08:31.545
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

08:33.513 --> 08:35.248
SEГ‘ORA.

08:35.248 --> 08:36.249
SEГ‘OR.

08:36.249 --> 08:37.384
HELLO, SIR.

08:37.384 --> 08:38.652
I'M OFFICER JESSICA TANG.

08:38.652 --> 08:40.654
IS THE OWNER OF THE HOUSE
AVAILABLE?

08:40.654 --> 08:43.624
OH, I AM SORRY.
MRS. WILLIAMS IS NOT HOME.

08:43.624 --> 08:45.726
IT'S OKAY, JOSГ©.
I GOT THIS.

08:45.726 --> 08:47.360
MR. WILLIAMS?

08:47.360 --> 08:49.029
YES.

08:49.029 --> 08:51.799
IS THIS ABOUT THE MARIJUANA?
'CAUSE I HAVE A CARD.

08:52.866 --> 08:54.434
UH, NO, SIR.
IT'S ABOUT YOUR WIFE.

08:54.434 --> 08:57.404
SHE'S WITH HER BOYFRIEND.
SHE WON'T BE HOME TILL TONIGHT.

08:57.404 --> 08:58.939
THERE WAS AN ACCIDENT.

08:58.939 --> 09:02.075
WE'RE STILL INVESTIGATING
THE CIRCUMSTANCES.

09:02.075 --> 09:05.579
WE BELIEVE YOUR WIFE WAS HIT
BY A CAR AND KILLED.

09:08.415 --> 09:10.584
DO YOU NEED
TO SIT DOWN, SIR?

09:10.584 --> 09:12.586
SHE'S DEAD?

09:12.586 --> 09:14.054
YES.

09:14.054 --> 09:15.623
I'M SORRY.

09:20.227 --> 09:22.295
SHE'S -- SHE'S DEAD.

09:22.295 --> 09:23.931
[ LAUGHS ]

09:23.931 --> 09:26.133
LA BRUJA ESTГЎ MUERTA.

09:26.133 --> 09:27.300
OH, MY GOD.

09:27.300 --> 09:28.702
LA BRUJA ESTГЎ MUERTA!

09:28.702 --> 09:30.203
"BRUJA ES M-MUERTA"?

09:30.203 --> 09:31.538
"THE WITCH IS DEAD."

09:31.538 --> 09:33.040
[ LAUGHS ]

09:33.040 --> 09:35.408
DING DONG, THIS IS SOME
STRANGE SHIT RIGHT HERE.

09:35.408 --> 09:36.810
[ LAUGHS ]

09:37.811 --> 09:38.812
AGAINST THE WALL,
CHERYL.

09:38.812 --> 09:40.013
I'M CRYSTAL NOW.

09:41.982 --> 09:44.151
SHE GOT A PIPE
STASHED SOMEWHERE.

09:44.151 --> 09:45.619
IT'S AN EASY FELONY.

09:45.619 --> 09:48.221
ONE GOOD HOOKER'S
WORTH 10 C.I.s.

09:48.221 --> 09:49.222
I SAY WE FLIP HER.

09:49.222 --> 09:50.323
SHE'S A KID.

09:50.323 --> 09:52.259
A LITTLE JAIL TIME,
SHE MIGHT GO STRAIGHT.

09:52.259 --> 09:54.194
LET SOMEBODY ELSE
PLAY CAPTAIN SAVE-A-HOE.

09:54.194 --> 09:56.363
THE PIPE GIVES US LEVERAGE.
I SAY WE USE IT.

09:56.363 --> 09:57.497
ALL RIGHT.

09:57.497 --> 09:59.466
HEY, CRYSTAL.
GIVE US THE PURSE.

09:59.466 --> 10:01.001
COME ON.

10:03.904 --> 10:05.372
Ben: LOOK AT THIS.

10:07.607 --> 10:10.110
[ SIGHS ]

10:10.110 --> 10:13.814
Sammy:
GIVE ME ONE GOOD REASON WHY
I SHOULDN'T TAKE YOU TO JAIL.

10:13.814 --> 10:15.749
'CAUSE RONNIE
WILL BEAT MY ASS.

10:15.749 --> 10:17.584
YOU DON'T THINK
I CAN SEE HIM

10:17.584 --> 10:19.252
PARKED OVER THERE
IN THAT CAR?

10:19.252 --> 10:22.189
YOU GOING TO JAIL
FUCKS WITH HIS MONEY.

10:22.189 --> 10:24.391
START TALKING.

10:25.926 --> 10:27.995
DAY DAY
GOT A STASH HOUSE.

10:27.995 --> 10:30.097
TWO TREY
DAY DAY CRAWFORD?

10:30.097 --> 10:33.834
YEAH.
OVER BY HIS SPOT ON DENKER.

10:34.802 --> 10:36.770
THANK YOU.

10:37.671 --> 10:39.973
HAVE A NICE DAY.

10:44.644 --> 10:47.247
SO, HOW LONG
YOU BEEN A COP?

10:50.417 --> 10:52.986
MARRIED? KIDS?

10:54.755 --> 10:56.189
DIVORCED?

10:56.189 --> 10:58.792
YOUR FEIGNED INTEREST
IN MY PERSONAL LIFE

10:58.792 --> 11:00.160
IS GONNA HAVE NO BEARING

11:00.160 --> 11:02.696
ON HOW I EVALUATE
YOUR STREET READINESS, OKAY?

11:02.696 --> 11:03.864
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:03.864 --> 11:05.833
THAT'S GOT TO BE
THE NICEST WAY

11:05.833 --> 11:08.301
ANYONE HAS EVER TOLD ME
TO SHUT UP.

11:10.237 --> 11:12.405
SO, NEVER MARRIED?

11:12.405 --> 11:15.442
OKAY, THEN.
SHUT UP.

11:18.278 --> 11:20.814
OOH, CHECK THIS GUY OUT.

11:20.814 --> 11:22.916
FULL MOON
IN BROAD DAYLIGHT.

11:24.317 --> 11:26.319
SIR?

11:26.319 --> 11:27.855
HEY.

11:27.855 --> 11:29.656
HEY, HOW'S IT HANGING,
BROTHER?

11:29.656 --> 11:30.791
OH, ROUGH MORNING.
YEAH.

11:30.791 --> 11:32.192
I'M A LITTLE UNDERWATER.

11:32.192 --> 11:34.561
UH, YOU KNOW YOU FORGOT
YOUR CLOTHES, RIGHT?

11:34.561 --> 11:37.030
I JUST NEEDED A RUN,
YOU KNOW?

11:37.030 --> 11:38.398
OKAY.

11:38.398 --> 11:41.334
WELL, YOU CAN'T RUN ON CITY
STREETS, BUT TAKE THE ON-RAMP.

11:41.334 --> 11:42.569
FREEWAYS ARE OKAY.

11:42.569 --> 11:45.072
OH.
GREAT. THANKS.

11:45.072 --> 11:49.342
CALL CHP.
HE'S THEIR PROBLEM NOW.

11:50.878 --> 11:52.479
HUNGRY?

11:52.479 --> 11:53.781
SO, NO MONEY WAS TAKEN?

11:53.781 --> 11:55.582
NO.
GUY CAME IN WITH A SKI MASK.

11:55.582 --> 11:59.019
HE WENT TO THE MAGAZINE RACK
AND [SNAPS FINGERS] SHOT HIM.

11:59.019 --> 12:00.687
Ruben:
HMM. HE RAN OFF?

12:00.687 --> 12:02.155
NO, NO.
HE STAYED CALM.

12:02.155 --> 12:05.025
HE WALKED OUT, BUT HE HAD
A LITTLE BIT OF A LIMP.

12:05.025 --> 12:07.294
DID YOU KNOW THE VICTIM?
[ SIGHS ]

12:07.294 --> 12:10.163
EVERY DAY, HE READS VARIETY.
HE NEVER PAYS.

12:10.163 --> 12:13.366
ALL HE TALKS ABOUT
IS AUDITIONS, JOBS, ACTING.

12:13.366 --> 12:14.701
I DON'T KNOW.

12:14.701 --> 12:17.838
LOOK, LET ME ASK YOU --
HOW LONG TILL MY STORE IS OPEN?

12:17.838 --> 12:22.675
IT'S GONNA BE A FEW HOURS, OKAY?
HOLD TIGHT.

12:22.675 --> 12:24.244
[ SIGHS ]

12:24.244 --> 12:25.979
PROBABLY ANOTHER
BROKE ACTOR.

12:25.979 --> 12:30.317
WHAT DID THEY SAY
WHEN YOU CALLED HIS I.D. IN?

12:30.317 --> 12:34.054
HAROLD MACK LOGAN.
MULTIPLE PAROLEE.

12:34.054 --> 12:37.524
THIS CAT'S RAP SHEET
IS THICKER THAN A POCKET BIBLE.

12:39.192 --> 12:43.196
YOU SEE THAT?
THE MARKS AROUND THE EDGES?

12:43.196 --> 12:44.197
MM-HMM.

12:45.999 --> 12:47.534
HEY.
[ SNAPS FINGERS ]

12:47.534 --> 12:49.069
OFF THE PHONE.
WHAT? WHAT?

12:49.069 --> 12:50.470
YOU MOPPED UP
THE FLOOR?

12:50.470 --> 12:52.906
WELL, I MEAN, DO YOU KNOW
HOW HARD IT IS

12:52.906 --> 12:55.208
TO GET BLOOD OUT OF TILE
ONCE IT SOAKS IN?

12:55.208 --> 12:57.544
ARE YOU GUYS
GOING TO PAY FOR MY FLOOR?

12:57.544 --> 12:58.879
[ SIGHS ]

12:58.879 --> 13:00.680
AND TO THINK I WAS GONNA
BUY A SLUSHIE FROM YOU.

13:00.680 --> 13:01.915
YOU'RE STUPID.

13:03.650 --> 13:05.819
Sammy:
I LIKE TORII HUNTER.

13:05.819 --> 13:08.956
Jones: MY MAN JaMARCUS
WILL SMOKE HIS ASS.

13:08.956 --> 13:10.690
THAT JERSEY IS CURSED.

13:10.690 --> 13:12.425
NO WAY.

13:15.095 --> 13:18.631
HOW CAN YOU SIT SO COMFORTABLY
WITH BALLS THAT BIG?

13:18.631 --> 13:19.732
[ LAUGHS ]

13:19.732 --> 13:23.103
I GOT YOUR $20
RIGHT HERE.

13:24.471 --> 13:25.672
BEN, YOU IN?

13:25.672 --> 13:27.140
Ben: I'M OUT.

13:27.140 --> 13:28.408
ANAWALT?

13:28.408 --> 13:31.611
SHOULDN'T WE BE FOCUSED
ON WHAT WE'RE GONNA DO?

13:31.611 --> 13:32.812
Jones: WE ARE.

13:32.812 --> 13:35.215
WE'RE HERE
TO PROTECT AND SERVE.

13:36.549 --> 13:38.351
AND KICK ASS.

13:42.822 --> 13:44.624
[ ENGINES TURN OVER ]

13:44.624 --> 13:49.296
Sammy: COME ON, TORII HUNTER.
LET'S SEE WHAT YOU GOT.

13:49.296 --> 13:50.864
HEY, FELLAS,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

13:50.864 --> 13:52.532
Man: FIVE-O!
FIVE-O! FIVE-O!

13:52.532 --> 13:53.566
NO, NO, NO!

13:53.566 --> 13:54.801
COME ON, TORII HUNTER.

13:54.801 --> 13:56.336
HEY!
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!

13:56.336 --> 13:59.106
STOP, STOP, STOP, STOP.
DOWN! GET DOWN!

13:59.106 --> 14:00.373
Anawalt: ON THE GROUND!
ON THE GROUND!

14:00.373 --> 14:01.841
HANDS OUT. OUT.
COME ON, TORII HUNTER.

14:01.841 --> 14:04.411
JaMARCUS IS COMING
FOR THAT ASS!

14:04.411 --> 14:05.578
JUST WIN, BABY!

14:05.578 --> 14:07.214
JUST WIN!

14:07.214 --> 14:08.748
HEY, I'M HAVING
A BAD DAY.

14:08.748 --> 14:09.983
I'M GONNA KEEP
THAT $20.

14:09.983 --> 14:11.051
TAKE IT EASY.

14:11.051 --> 14:12.485
HOW'S EVERYBODY
DOING TODAY?

14:12.485 --> 14:14.387
GET UP.

14:14.387 --> 14:16.189
YOUR BOY CAN'T RUN
FOR SHIT, MAN.

14:16.189 --> 14:18.158
ALL RIGHT. LET'S GO.
HOW MANY WE GOT?

14:18.158 --> 14:19.559
HUH? HOW MANY WE GOT?

14:19.559 --> 14:21.728
FOUR.
Anawalt: STAY RIGHT HERE.
RIGHT HERE.

14:21.728 --> 14:22.996
FOUR.

14:22.996 --> 14:24.497
THE FUCK DID YOU LEARN
HOW TO COUNT?

14:24.497 --> 14:25.765
I COUNT THREE.

14:25.765 --> 14:28.268
I GOT ONE. ANAWALT, YOU HAD TWO.
WHERE'S YOUR OTHER ONE?

14:28.268 --> 14:30.537
YEAH, I GOT --
DID WE LOSE SOMEBODY?

14:30.537 --> 14:31.771
UM...

14:31.771 --> 14:35.008
Jones: THE LAST GUY YOU GOT,
WHEN YOU ARRESTED HIM,

14:35.008 --> 14:37.744
ARE YOU SURE YOU HEARD
THE CUFFS CLICK?

14:37.744 --> 14:39.679
UM, I...

14:39.679 --> 14:41.514
Sammy:
WE LOST SOMEBODY?

14:41.514 --> 14:42.950
I...

14:42.950 --> 14:45.385
I MEAN, HE HAD TO HAVE GONE
THAT WAY. LET'S SMOKE HIM OUT.

14:45.385 --> 14:47.720
Ben: ALL RIGHT.
LET'S GO. HERE.

14:47.720 --> 14:49.289
HE HAD TO --

14:49.289 --> 14:50.490
OH, SHIT.

14:50.490 --> 14:52.926
Lydia: SO, WHAT
DOES OUR VICTIM'S RAP SHEET

14:52.926 --> 14:53.961
TELL US ABOUT HIM?

14:53.961 --> 14:57.164
DESPITE 12 DRUG BUSTS,

14:57.164 --> 14:59.766
LOGAN'S NEVER DONE
MORE THAN A TWO-YEAR STRETCH.

14:59.766 --> 15:01.201
MANDATORY SENTENCING

15:01.201 --> 15:05.338
SHOULD HAVE HAD THIS CAT AWAY
FOR DECADES LONGER.

15:05.338 --> 15:06.706
HE'S A SNITCH.
SNITCH.

15:06.706 --> 15:08.908
[ CHUCKLES ]
SO, WHAT
ARE YOU THINKING?

15:08.908 --> 15:10.410
SOMEBODY HE SNITCHED ON
POPPED HIM?

15:10.410 --> 15:11.945
IT'S A GOOD PLACE
TO START.

15:11.945 --> 15:14.948
I MEAN, ALL THOSE ARRESTS,
HE'S GOT LOTS OF ENEMIES.

15:14.948 --> 15:16.483
THANK YOU.

15:16.483 --> 15:18.585
LOGAN IS NOT IN OUR DATABASE
AS A PAID C.I.

15:18.585 --> 15:20.353
WELL, LET'S THINK
OUTSIDE THE BOX.

15:20.353 --> 15:22.055
WHAT TOOLS
WOULD YOU HAVE USED

15:22.055 --> 15:23.890
WHEN YOU WERE
ON THE ROBBERY TABLE?

15:23.890 --> 15:25.658
GOOGLE. [ CHUCKLES ]

15:25.658 --> 15:27.160
COME ON.

15:27.160 --> 15:28.828
IF IT WERE THAT EASY,
ANYBODY COULD WORK HOMICIDE.

15:28.828 --> 15:29.929
[ LYDIA SCOFFS ]

15:29.929 --> 15:31.531
IF IT WERE THAT HARD,
DO YOU THINK

15:31.531 --> 15:33.533
A JARHEAD LIKE YOU
COULD DO IT?

15:33.533 --> 15:35.702
[ LAUGHS ]

15:35.702 --> 15:37.437
DARRELL MILLER.

15:37.437 --> 15:38.671
MM-HMM.

15:38.671 --> 15:40.840
ALWAYS MAINTAINED HIS INNOCENCE.
WHAT ELSE IS NEW?

15:40.840 --> 15:45.712
UH, CONVICTED ON THE TESTIMONY
OF A JAILHOUSE SNITCH.

15:45.712 --> 15:47.080
IT'S OUR GUY,
MACK LOGAN.

15:47.080 --> 15:48.381
MM-HMM.

15:48.381 --> 15:51.151
AND MILLER WAS FREED
WHEN THEY FINALLY BOTHERED

15:51.151 --> 15:53.220
TO DO A DNA TEST
ON OLD EVIDENCE.

15:53.220 --> 15:55.488
RELEASED EIGHT MONTHS AGO.

15:55.488 --> 15:58.691
"MY LORD AND SAVIOR,
JESUS CHRIST.

15:58.691 --> 16:00.393
I HOLD NO GRUDGES."

16:00.393 --> 16:03.096
22 YEARS?
WE'LL SEE ABOUT THAT.

16:03.096 --> 16:05.265
WHY YOU BEING SO HARD
ON ANAWALT?

16:05.265 --> 16:07.467
HUH?
NEVER LOST
A SUSPECT BEFORE?

16:07.467 --> 16:10.003
PLEAD THE FIFTH.
MM.

16:10.003 --> 16:12.272
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

16:12.272 --> 16:14.407
REMEMBER,
FOR YOUR NEXT JOB,

16:14.407 --> 16:18.245
THE REGULAR McNUGGET MEAL COMES
WITH SIX NUGGETS, NOT FOUR,

16:18.245 --> 16:20.480
PLUS FRIES AND A DRINK.

16:25.885 --> 16:27.787
IS THAT YOURS?

16:27.787 --> 16:29.889
YEAH.

16:29.889 --> 16:31.891
LET ME SEE IT.

16:31.891 --> 16:33.826
Ben:
IS THIS GHETTO CINDERELLA?

16:33.826 --> 16:36.229
ANAWALT MATCHES HER SHOE,
FINDS A PRINCE?

16:36.229 --> 16:37.597
KISS MY ASS, SHERMAN.

16:37.597 --> 16:39.566
OOH, LANGUAGE.
THE CHERUB HAS TENDER EARS.

16:39.566 --> 16:41.568
Jones:
NO WAY SOMEBODY LEAVES BEHIND

16:41.568 --> 16:44.571
A BRAND-NEW, CUSTOMIZED TENNIS
SHOE UNLESS THEY ON THE RUN.

16:44.571 --> 16:46.106
SEE THE INITIALS
ON THE BACK?

16:46.106 --> 16:48.941
WHAT'S THAT STAND FOR?
"ASSHOLE RUNNING"?

16:48.941 --> 16:50.043
"ANAWALT'S REGRET"?

16:50.043 --> 16:51.378
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:51.378 --> 16:54.047
YOU KNOW WHO'S WEARING
THE OTHER SNEAKER?

16:54.047 --> 16:56.316
I AIN'T NO SNITCH.

16:56.316 --> 16:58.918
WHAT IF I BUY YOU
A HAPPY MEAL

16:58.918 --> 17:02.021
AND LET YOU PLAY WITH THE SIREN
IN THE PATROL CAR?

17:05.658 --> 17:07.527
FOLLOW ME.

17:08.161 --> 17:10.730
GIVE ME MY SHOE.

17:16.536 --> 17:18.171
GET OUT OF HERE.

17:21.941 --> 17:24.277
POLICE OFFICERS!

17:26.146 --> 17:28.648
HOW Y'ALL DOING?

17:30.450 --> 17:33.686
I'M SORRY
TO BOTHER YOU, MA'AM.

17:33.686 --> 17:35.822
DOES THIS SHOE
LOOK FAMILIAR?

17:35.822 --> 17:36.823
NO.

17:36.823 --> 17:38.591
CLEAR IN HERE.

17:40.026 --> 17:41.494
HE'S RUNNING!

17:45.298 --> 17:48.101
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

17:49.702 --> 17:51.471
WHAT THE HELL,
YOU DAMN ASSHOLE?

17:51.471 --> 17:53.573
HIT ME WITH A BASEBALL BAT?
YOU COULD HAVE KILLED ME!

17:53.573 --> 17:56.776
Anawalt: BEN, I GOT IT.
HELL YOU THINKING
ABOUT, MAN?

17:56.776 --> 17:57.577
HUH?
COME ON.

17:57.577 --> 17:58.945
IS HE YOUR SON?
NO.

17:58.945 --> 18:01.381
IS HE YOUR BROTHER?
YOUR COUSIN? YOUR NEPHEW?

18:01.381 --> 18:02.382
I DON'T KNOW HIM.

18:02.382 --> 18:03.550
YOU DON'T KNOW HIM?

18:03.550 --> 18:05.152
AND YOU LET HIM HIDE
IN YOUR HOUSE?

18:05.152 --> 18:06.853
HE'S MORE MY PEOPLE
THAN YOU.
LET'S GO. COME ON.

18:06.853 --> 18:09.289
YOU SEE IF WE EVER RESPOND
TO A CALL FROM THIS HOUSE AGAIN.

18:09.289 --> 18:10.657
NOBODY ASKED YOU
TO COME OVER HERE.

18:10.657 --> 18:12.325
NOBODY A-- WE'RE OVER HERE
EVERY DAY, LADY!

18:12.325 --> 18:14.060
GET THE HELL OFF MY PROPERTY!
I DON'T CARE!

18:14.060 --> 18:16.463
EVERY DAY,
WE'RE IN THIS NEIGHBORHOOD!
Sammy: HEY, HEY, HEY!

18:16.463 --> 18:18.231
EVERY FUCKING DAY
WE'RE HERE!
OH, HELL, NO!

18:18.231 --> 18:19.932
WHAT THE FUCK YOU TALKING
ABOUT?! WE'RE HERE!

18:19.932 --> 18:21.268
SHERMAN, LET'S GO.

18:21.268 --> 18:22.735
YOU GOT SOMEBODY YOU WANT ME
TO CALL, HONEY?

18:22.735 --> 18:23.670
NO, MA'AM. THANK YOU.

18:23.670 --> 18:25.071
OH, YOU'RE
POLITE NOW, HUH?!

18:25.071 --> 18:26.839
COME ON, SHERMAN.
LET'S GO.
FUCK.

18:27.774 --> 18:31.211
YOU EVER
GONNA LET ME DRIVE?
NO.

18:31.211 --> 18:32.412
[ CHUCKLES ]

18:32.412 --> 18:34.347
WHAT ABOUT
AFTER EVALUATION?

18:34.347 --> 18:37.250
HOW'D YOU HURT
YOUR BACK?

18:37.250 --> 18:38.718
OH, I SEE.

18:38.718 --> 18:41.020
ANYTHING I ASK YOU,
I GET STONEWALLED.

18:41.020 --> 18:43.756
BUT I'M SUPPOSED TO BE
AN OPEN BOOK.

18:43.756 --> 18:44.757
I'M THE ONE

18:44.757 --> 18:46.326
IN THE DRIVER'S SEAT.

18:46.326 --> 18:47.927
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA,
WHOA, WHOA.

18:47.927 --> 18:49.128
HOLY SHIT.
OH, MY GOD!

18:49.128 --> 18:50.763
[ SIREN WAILING ]

18:50.763 --> 18:52.265
857.

18:52.265 --> 18:55.001
REQUEST AN R.A. UNIT,
OUR LOCATION,

18:55.001 --> 18:57.637
1600 BLOCK,
NORTH CAHUENGA.

18:57.637 --> 18:59.172
[ WAILING STOPS ]

19:00.440 --> 19:02.041
857.

19:02.041 --> 19:05.212
SEND AN R.A. UNIT, OUR LOCATION,
1600 BLOCK CAHUENGA BOULEVARD.

19:05.212 --> 19:08.114
SHOW US CODE SIX
AT 1643 NORTH CAHUENGA.

19:08.114 --> 19:10.016
YOU GOT A BLANKET
IN THE TRUNK?

19:10.016 --> 19:11.584
I LOVE BALDWIN HILLS.
YEAH.

19:11.584 --> 19:13.320
JUST 'CAUSE
IT'S SOUTH L.A.

19:13.320 --> 19:15.822
DOESN'T MEAN IT HAS TO BE
RUN-DOWN, RIGHT?

19:15.822 --> 19:16.823
UH-HUH.

19:23.230 --> 19:25.232
MAY I HELP YOU,
DETECTIVES?

19:25.232 --> 19:26.833
YOU DARRELL D. MILLER?

19:26.833 --> 19:29.068
YEP.

19:29.068 --> 19:30.937
YOU KNOW THIS MAN?

19:30.937 --> 19:33.840
MACK LOGAN? YEAH.

19:33.840 --> 19:37.810
LIED ON ME AND ROBBED ME
OF TWO DECADES OF SUNSHINE.

19:37.810 --> 19:39.279
WHAT DID HE DO NOW?

19:39.279 --> 19:42.949
WAS SHOT AT POINT-BLANK RANGE
NOT EVEN 10 MINUTES FROM HERE.

19:42.949 --> 19:45.352
YOU KNOW,
L.A.'s A DANGEROUS PLACE.

19:45.352 --> 19:47.086
WHERE WERE YOU
THIS MORNING?

19:47.086 --> 19:50.357
I WAS HELPING MY GRANDMOTHER
WITH HER PILL REGIMEN.

19:50.357 --> 19:52.492
SHE'S 93.
I TAKE CARE OF HER NOW.

19:52.492 --> 19:55.127
OKAY. AND SHE'LL
VOUCH FOR YOU ON THAT?

19:55.127 --> 19:58.665
YOU KNOW, I HATED THAT FOOL.
THAT AIN'T NO SECRET.

19:58.665 --> 20:00.767
MACK SAID I CONFESSED
UP AT COUNTY

20:00.767 --> 20:03.670
TO RAPING SOME WHITE WOMAN
I HADN'T EVEN MET

20:03.670 --> 20:06.339
JUST SO HE COULD GO HOME
THREE YEARS EARLY.

20:06.339 --> 20:09.075
MY MOTHER DIED
THINKING I WAS A RAPIST.

20:09.075 --> 20:10.743
IF NOT
FOR THAT DNA STUFF,

20:10.743 --> 20:13.946
I'D STILL BE DOING TIME
FOR HIM RIGHT NOW.

20:16.015 --> 20:17.884
Woman: DARRELL?

20:17.884 --> 20:21.454
WHY DON'T YOU OFFER YOUR FRIENDS
SOME LEMONADE?

20:21.454 --> 20:24.524
THAT'S OKAY, GRAN-GRAN.
THEY WAS JUST LEAVING.

20:24.524 --> 20:28.261
HEY, IN CASE
YOU THINK OF SOMETHING ELSE.

20:28.261 --> 20:29.862
THANKS.

20:31.664 --> 20:33.400
I DON'T KNOW.
SAW THAT LIMP?

20:33.400 --> 20:35.067
MM-HMM.
JUST LIKE IN THE VIDEO.

20:35.067 --> 20:38.237
YOU THINK GRAN-GRAN WILL CHANGE
HER STORY WHEN HE LEAVES,

20:38.237 --> 20:41.608
LET US HAVE A LOOK
INSIDE?

20:41.608 --> 20:44.010
[ SCOFFS ] HOPE SO.

20:45.745 --> 20:48.214
"HE'S MORE MY PEOPLE
THAN YOU."

20:48.214 --> 20:49.616
SHE'S RIGHT.

20:49.616 --> 20:52.552
THEY DON'T WANT US THERE.
I DON'T WANT TO BE THERE.

20:52.552 --> 20:55.855
ANOTHER SECOND, A FEW INCHES
LOWER, I'D BE DEAD RIGHT NOW.

20:57.890 --> 21:01.193
WHEN I WAS YOUNGER,
THAT'S ALL THE L.A.P.D. DID

21:01.193 --> 21:03.296
WAS CONSTANTLY
KICK OUR ASSES.

21:03.296 --> 21:06.499
THAT'S WHERE I REMEMBER
RUCKER --

21:06.499 --> 21:08.267
THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

21:08.267 --> 21:10.903
SO, WHY BECOME A COP?

21:13.406 --> 21:17.344
THERE WAS A S.W.A.T. OFFICER
CAME AND SPOKE TO OUR SCHOOL.

21:17.344 --> 21:19.145
RANDY SIMMONS.

21:20.246 --> 21:25.352
SOMETHING ABOUT THE WAY DUDE
CARRIED HIMSELF STUCK WITH ME.

21:25.352 --> 21:27.186
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

21:27.186 --> 21:29.756
MY UNCLE WAS A COP.

21:31.157 --> 21:33.793
MY FRIENDS AND I WERE STONED.
I SIGNED UP AS A GOOF.

21:33.793 --> 21:36.396
SEEMED LIKE A GOOD IDEA
AT THE TIME.

21:36.396 --> 21:38.030
[ LAUGHTER ]

21:39.766 --> 21:42.168
I WANTED TO MAKE
A DIFFERENCE.

21:42.168 --> 21:43.636
ANOTHER GHETTO TOURIST.

21:43.636 --> 21:45.938
IT WAS EITHER THIS
OR TEACH FOR AMERICA.

21:45.938 --> 21:48.341
AND HAVE YOU CHANGED
ANYBODY'S LIFE?

21:49.576 --> 21:53.480
YOU KNOW, IT'S FUNNY.
I USED TO --

21:53.480 --> 21:55.948
I USED TO THINK
ABOUT HOW THESE KIDS GREW UP.

21:55.948 --> 22:00.653
NO PARENTS,
DRUG ABUSE, HUNGRY.

22:00.653 --> 22:02.955
AND NOW?

22:03.890 --> 22:05.758
I AIN'T
A SOCIAL WORKER.

22:05.758 --> 22:09.529
[ LAUGHS ] WHEN DID CAPTAIN
SAVE-A-HOE BECOME A LIBERTARIAN?

22:09.529 --> 22:11.864
I GUESS THAT BIT WITH THE BAT
CHANGED MY MIND.

22:11.864 --> 22:13.099
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:13.099 --> 22:14.534
WELL, YOU MAY BECOME
A DECENT COP YET, SHERMAN.

22:14.534 --> 22:16.235
OH, THANK YOU VERY MUCH,
BRYANT.

22:16.235 --> 22:17.770
HE'S VERY CHARITABLE
THIS MORNING.

22:17.770 --> 22:19.439
DISPATCHER:
Any available unit,

22:19.439 --> 22:22.609
neighbor dispute
at 2233 83rd Street.

22:22.609 --> 22:24.611
Handling unit, identify.

22:24.611 --> 22:26.379
836.
SHOW US HANDLING.

22:26.379 --> 22:27.580
DO YOU WANT THIS?

22:27.580 --> 22:29.616
I DON'T WANT THIS.
UGH.

22:30.517 --> 22:32.719
Lydia: COME ON, NOW.

22:36.923 --> 22:40.126
LET'S LET HIM GET A LITTLE
FURTHER DOWN THE BLOCK.

22:43.963 --> 22:46.599
WHAT DO WE SAY TO THE OLD LADY
WHEN WE GET THERE?

22:46.599 --> 22:49.969
WE JUST
INTRODUCE OURSELVES.

22:49.969 --> 22:51.003
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

22:51.003 --> 22:52.605
YEAH, LET'S GO.

22:56.609 --> 22:58.144
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

23:00.112 --> 23:03.583
I'M SORRY, MRS. MILLER,
TO BOTHER YOU AGAIN.

23:03.583 --> 23:06.385
UM, I'M
DETECTIVE LYDIA ADAMS.

23:06.385 --> 23:07.687
BRENDA!

23:07.687 --> 23:10.322
HOW YOU DOING, GIRL?

23:10.322 --> 23:13.225
HEY!
HOW YOU DOING?

23:13.225 --> 23:14.961
JUST CAME BY
TO CHECK ON YOU.

23:14.961 --> 23:16.996
DARRELL
WENT TO THE STORE.

23:16.996 --> 23:17.964
OH.

23:17.964 --> 23:20.299
YOU KNOW,
I ALWAYS LIKED YOU.

23:20.299 --> 23:22.735
I SAID
HAD DARRELL MARRIED YOU,

23:22.735 --> 23:25.472
NONE OF THAT OTHER MESS
WOULD HAVE HAPPENED.

23:26.706 --> 23:28.708
YOU REMEMBER RUBEN,
RIGHT?

23:28.708 --> 23:30.309
YEAH. HE GOT TALL.

23:30.309 --> 23:33.312
[ CHUCKLES ]
HI. HOW YOU DOING?

23:33.312 --> 23:35.414
UM, DARRELL BORROWED...

23:35.414 --> 23:37.283
RUBEN'S ICE CUBE T-SHIRT

23:37.283 --> 23:39.852
[CHUCKLES] A WHILE AGO,
AND HE WANTS IT BACK.

23:39.852 --> 23:41.821
DO YOU MIND IF WE CHECK
HIS ROOM?

23:41.821 --> 23:44.591
OH, BABY, YOU AIN'T GONNA FIND
NOTHING BACK THERE.

23:44.591 --> 23:47.594
JUST AS MESSY AS ALWAYS.
I'M STILL DOING HIS LAUNDRY.

23:47.594 --> 23:50.429
DO YOU MIND IF WE CHECK
THE LAUNDRY ROOM?

23:50.429 --> 23:51.531
GO RIGHT AHEAD.

23:51.531 --> 23:53.733
LAUNDRY ROOM
IS BY THE KITCHEN.

23:53.733 --> 23:55.267
OH, OKAY. THANK YOU.

23:55.267 --> 23:57.203
Y'ALL WANT
SOME LEMONADE?

23:57.203 --> 23:59.572
MM-HMM. YEAH.
SURE.

23:59.572 --> 24:02.408
BABY, WHAT DID YOU SAY
YOUR NAME WAS, AGAIN?

24:02.408 --> 24:05.311
DETECTIVE LYDIA ADAMS.

24:05.311 --> 24:06.879
OKAY, BRENDA.

24:06.879 --> 24:09.849
I'LL GET THAT LEMONADE
BEFORE MY STORIES COME BACK ON.

24:09.849 --> 24:11.217
OKAY.

24:12.652 --> 24:14.086
ARE YOU SURE
WE CAN DO THIS?

24:14.086 --> 24:15.855
DARRELL CAN'T HAVE IT
BOTH WAYS.

24:15.855 --> 24:18.691
IF GRANNY IS COMPETENT ENOUGH
TO BE HIS ALIBI,

24:18.691 --> 24:21.360
SHE'S COMPETENT ENOUGH
TO GIVE US CONSENT.

24:21.360 --> 24:23.062
Tang: HEY.

24:23.062 --> 24:24.463
HEY, MAN.

24:24.463 --> 24:27.634
UM, RIGHT BACK HERE.

24:27.634 --> 24:31.237
ALL RIGHT, SO DUDE'S BACK HERE
IN THE BOOTH, RIGHT?

24:31.237 --> 24:34.941
JUST ABOUT THE TIME
THINGS ARE GETTING ENJOYABLE,

24:34.941 --> 24:35.942
BOOM!

24:35.942 --> 24:37.176
UP IN SMOKE.

24:37.176 --> 24:38.945
UP IN SMOKE IS RIGHT.

24:38.945 --> 24:40.379
John: HIS CLOTHES
SMELLED LIKE METH.

24:40.379 --> 24:42.949
HE'S PROBABLY LOADED
WITH FLAMMABLE CHEMICALS.

24:42.949 --> 24:44.684
WONDER WHAT
HE WAS WATCHING.

24:44.684 --> 24:46.653
THAT SHIT MUST HAVE
GOT HOT, RIGHT?

24:46.653 --> 24:47.654
[ LAUGHS ]

24:47.654 --> 24:49.021
Dewey: HEY, MAN.

24:49.021 --> 24:50.723
WHAT ARE
YOU GUYS INTO?

24:50.723 --> 24:51.824
HUH?
[ SIGHS ]

24:51.824 --> 24:53.425
COME ON.
YOU CAN TELL ME.

24:53.425 --> 24:56.262
LEAST I CAN ASK NOW THAT
CHICKIE'S IN METRO, RIGHT?

24:56.262 --> 24:57.496
WE'RE CITIZENS.

24:57.496 --> 24:59.666
COME ON, NOW.
WHAT ARE YOU INTO, GIRL?

24:59.666 --> 25:02.501
LIKE, ME,
I LIKE THE LARGE LADIES.

25:02.501 --> 25:05.271
SOFA-SIZED, MAN.
THE B.B.W.s

25:05.271 --> 25:06.539
THE WHAT?

25:06.539 --> 25:08.708
B.B.W.s, MAN.
BIG, BEAUTIFUL WOMEN.

25:08.708 --> 25:10.342
I'M GONNA WAIT
OUTSIDE.

25:10.342 --> 25:11.811
MORE OUNCE
TO THE BOUNCE.

25:11.811 --> 25:13.980
GIVE ME THEM
TIG OLD BITTIES.

25:13.980 --> 25:16.583
I SWEAR TO GOD, MAN,
FAT CHICKS ARE AWESOME.

25:16.583 --> 25:18.384
KIND OF LIKE
RIDING A MOPED.

25:18.384 --> 25:19.786
MOPED.
YEAH.

25:19.786 --> 25:23.255
IT'S FUN AS HELL
TILL SOMEONE CATCHES YOU ON ONE.

25:23.255 --> 25:25.157
[ LAUGHS ]

25:25.157 --> 25:26.593
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:26.593 --> 25:28.394
RIGHT?

25:28.394 --> 25:29.729
FUCK.

25:37.770 --> 25:39.405
WHAT'S GOING ON, PAOLO?

25:39.405 --> 25:41.641
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT -- THAT OLD
BITCH IS OFF HER MEDS AGAIN.

25:41.641 --> 25:42.975
EXCUSE ME, MA'AM?

25:42.975 --> 25:45.111
HER CATS ALWAYS GET OUT,
COMES OVER TO OUR YARD,

25:45.111 --> 25:47.113
CRAPS IN OUR SANDBOX
LIKE IT'S A LITTER BOX.

25:47.113 --> 25:48.848
MY 4-YEAR-OLD
DON'T KNOW NO BETTER.

25:48.848 --> 25:50.817
COMES HOME EVERY DAY
COVERED IN CAT SHIT.

25:50.817 --> 25:52.752
HAVE YOU FILED A COMPLAINT,
MA'AM?

25:52.752 --> 25:54.153
YES. NUMEROUS TIMES.

25:54.153 --> 25:56.388
BUT TODAY, I WENT OVER THERE
TO TALK TO HER,

25:56.388 --> 25:57.456
AND SHE SHOT AT ME!

25:57.456 --> 25:58.457
WHAT?

25:58.457 --> 26:00.226
I HEARD A GUNSHOT.

26:00.226 --> 26:01.594
YOU SAW A GUN?

26:01.594 --> 26:03.830
NO.
I HEARD A GUNSHOT.

26:03.830 --> 26:06.432
THAT OLD BITCH
FIRED AT ME.

26:06.432 --> 26:07.600
THAT'S WHY
I CALLED Y'ALL.

26:07.600 --> 26:08.901
DID YOU CHECK THIS OUT,
PAOLO?

26:08.901 --> 26:10.870
NO. GOT HERE
TWO MINUTES BEFORE YOU DID.

26:12.639 --> 26:14.273
IT'S JUST AN OLD LADY.

26:14.273 --> 26:17.209
YEAH.

26:17.209 --> 26:18.344
THANK YOU, MA'AM.

26:18.344 --> 26:22.114
WE'LL BE IN TOUCH
IF WE NEED ANYTHING ELSE.

26:29.521 --> 26:31.590
CAN YOU SEE?

26:33.626 --> 26:35.862
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

26:35.862 --> 26:37.964
MA'AM, IT'S THE POLICE.

26:37.964 --> 26:39.365
GUN! GUN!

26:39.365 --> 26:40.700
[ GUNSHOTS ]

26:46.739 --> 26:49.642
Sammy: 836.
SHOTS FIRED AT OUR LOCATION.

26:49.642 --> 26:51.811
REQUESTING
ADDITIONAL UNITS.

26:51.811 --> 26:53.212
WHAT'S HAPPENED?

26:53.212 --> 26:54.346
SHE HAS A GUN.

26:54.346 --> 26:57.283
SAW IT FROM THE REFLECTION
IN THE WINDOW.

26:57.283 --> 26:58.751
NOW SHE'S BARRICADED.

26:58.751 --> 27:00.452
DID ANYBODY
CALL S.W.A.T.?
NO.

27:00.452 --> 27:03.522
THAT REQUEST HAS TO COME
DIRECTLY FROM CAPTAIN RUCKER.

27:03.522 --> 27:04.590
[ LAUGHS ]

27:04.590 --> 27:06.192
WHAT?
WHAT'S SO FUNNY, MAN?

27:06.192 --> 27:08.661
WELL, YOU CAN'T HEAR
THE THEME MUSIC?

27:08.661 --> 27:10.529
HERE COMES SHAFT.

27:10.529 --> 27:12.631
NO MASK, NO WEAPON.

27:12.631 --> 27:16.202
WELL, IF THE BLOOD
ON THE SNEAKERS MATCHES LOGAN'S

27:16.202 --> 27:18.938
OR THE CLOTHES TEST POSITIVE
WITH GUNSHOT RESIDUE,

27:18.938 --> 27:21.140
WE'VE GOT ENOUGH P.C.
FOR AN ARREST.

27:21.140 --> 27:22.709
[ SIGHS ]

27:22.709 --> 27:24.276
WHAT'S BOTHERING YOU?

27:24.276 --> 27:28.380
HOMICIDE IS JUST DIFFERENT
THAN I THOUGHT IT WAS GONNA BE.

27:28.380 --> 27:29.448
YEAH?

27:29.448 --> 27:32.284
YEAH.
ALL THE LYING, WORD GAMES.

27:32.284 --> 27:34.186
IF DARRELL KILLED
MACK LOGAN,

27:34.186 --> 27:36.222
DON'T YOU THINK
HE HAD IT COMING?

27:36.222 --> 27:38.825
WHO THE HELL KNOWS WHAT
DARRELL WENT THROUGH IN PRISON?

27:38.825 --> 27:41.127
YEAH, BUT THAT'S NOT
DARRELL'S CHOICE TO MAKE.

27:58.410 --> 28:01.714
Ben:
JESUS. CHECK THIS OUT.

28:08.387 --> 28:10.957
SIR, YOU MIGHT
WANT TO TAKE COVER.

28:10.957 --> 28:13.492
YOU PULLED ME OUT OF
A CITY COUNCIL BANQUET FOR THIS?

28:13.492 --> 28:16.562
SHE'S NOT COMING OUT, SIR.
WE APPROACHED THE FRONT DOOR.

28:16.562 --> 28:18.197
SHE FIRED AT US.
WE NEED S.W.A.T.

28:18.197 --> 28:20.432
I GOT YOUR S.W.A.T.
RIGHT HERE.

28:20.432 --> 28:23.836
I'M NOT CALLING METRO
FOR SOME LITTLE OLD LADY.

28:23.836 --> 28:25.905
ANAWALT!
Anawalt: YES, SIR.

28:25.905 --> 28:27.974
YOU HAVE HER
ON THE PHONE?
YEAH.

28:27.974 --> 28:30.309
WE ROUTED ALL OUTGOING CALLS
TO MY CELLPHONE.

28:30.309 --> 28:32.178
WHO'S SHE CALLING FOR?
PASTORS.

28:32.178 --> 28:34.747
SHE DIDN'T REALIZE
SHE WAS TALKING TO ME

28:34.747 --> 28:36.015
EVERY TIME SHE CALLED.

28:36.015 --> 28:38.284
SHE ALSO WANTS FOOD
FOR HER CAT.

28:39.185 --> 28:40.586
SHERMAN.

28:40.586 --> 28:41.754
SIR?

28:41.754 --> 28:44.456
BLACK CASE
IN MY TRUNK, PLEASE.

28:44.456 --> 28:46.425
YES, SIR.

28:50.096 --> 28:52.531
IT SOUNDED LIKE
A VERY BIG GUN.

28:52.531 --> 28:53.766
YES, I'M SURE.

28:53.766 --> 28:55.434
AND -- AND SHE FIRED
AT US.
YES.

28:55.434 --> 28:57.804
YES, YES, YES.
THANK YOU, BRYANT.

29:03.409 --> 29:06.412
BLESSED IS SHE...

29:06.412 --> 29:10.082
WHOSE TRANSGRESSION
IS FORGIVEN,

29:10.082 --> 29:12.484
WHOSE SIN IS COVERED!

29:12.484 --> 29:14.987
BLESSED IS THE WOMAN

29:14.987 --> 29:20.159
TO WHOM THE LORD
DOES NOT IMPUTE INIQUITY

29:20.159 --> 29:24.897
AND IN WHOSE SPIRIT
THERE IS NO DECEIT!

29:24.897 --> 29:26.765
[ GUN COCKS ]

29:26.765 --> 29:30.202
Woman:
COME ANY CLOSER, I'LL SHOOT.

29:30.202 --> 29:32.171
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
SHERMAN!

29:32.171 --> 29:33.940
SIR, JUST GIVE ME A SECOND.
HEY, COME HERE.

29:33.940 --> 29:35.241
[ CAT MEOWS ]
COME HERE.

29:35.241 --> 29:36.876
MA'AM!

29:36.876 --> 29:38.911
MA'AM, WE HAVE YOUR CAT.

29:38.911 --> 29:40.913
WE HAVE HER OUT
RIGHT HERE.

29:40.913 --> 29:42.815
IF YOU DON'T COME OUT
IN THE NEXT 20 SECONDS,

29:42.815 --> 29:44.083
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO --

29:44.083 --> 29:45.217
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO
CALL THE POUND.

29:45.217 --> 29:46.986
YOU'RE NEVER
GONNA SEE HER AGAIN.

29:49.055 --> 29:50.522
[ CAT MEOWING ]

29:53.592 --> 29:55.027
PUT DOWN THE GUN, MA'AM.

29:55.027 --> 29:56.863
MA'AM, PUT DOWN THE GUN,
AND I'LL GIVE HER BACK TO YOU.

29:56.863 --> 29:57.897
WHAT'S THE CAT'S --

29:57.897 --> 29:58.965
Woman:
DON'T HURT HER.

29:58.965 --> 30:00.032
OKAY.
WHAT'S THE CAT'S NAME?

30:00.032 --> 30:02.801
SPOOKY.
SPOOKY. OKAY.

30:02.801 --> 30:05.071
I'LL -- THERE YOU GO.

30:05.071 --> 30:06.906
SPOOKY.
[ CAT MEOWS ]

30:06.906 --> 30:07.940
SPOOKY. OKAY.

30:07.940 --> 30:09.208
Rucker: GUN!

30:19.751 --> 30:22.088
KEVLAR. DAMN.

30:22.088 --> 30:23.622
THE BIT WITH THE CAT
WAS SMART.

30:23.622 --> 30:26.058
THANKS, MAN. ALWAYS
GOT TO THINK ON YOUR FEET.

30:26.058 --> 30:28.760
SHE WAS READY
TO GO TO WAR.

30:28.760 --> 30:30.196
GET HER UP.

30:30.196 --> 30:34.000
[ Chuckling ]
GRANBO AIN'T NO JOKE.

30:40.072 --> 30:42.308
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

30:44.376 --> 30:48.347
I CANNOT BELIEVE THE BLOOD
MATCHED THE SNEAKERS.

30:48.347 --> 30:51.517
NOW, GUILT NEVER SURPRISES ME.
ONLY INNOCENCE DOES.

30:51.517 --> 30:54.453
YOU GUYS, GO AROUND THE BACK.
WE'LL TAKE THE FRONT.

31:00.326 --> 31:03.129
OH, NO.
MOTHERFUCKER.

31:16.808 --> 31:17.743
[ GRUNTS ]

31:17.743 --> 31:18.877
AAH!

31:18.877 --> 31:20.479
HO! WHOA.

31:20.479 --> 31:21.713
HUH?

31:21.713 --> 31:22.982
HUH?

31:24.216 --> 31:25.417
COME ON.

31:25.417 --> 31:26.885
EASY.

31:30.022 --> 31:31.857
I COULD HAVE
SHOT YOU ALREADY.

31:31.857 --> 31:33.125
WHAT YOU WAITING FOR?

31:34.026 --> 31:35.461
[ GRUNTS ]

31:47.906 --> 31:50.576
YEAH, YOU DID IT.

31:50.576 --> 31:53.045
[ LYDIA SIGHS ]

31:54.446 --> 31:57.183
CALL SAID
IT WAS AROUND HERE SOMEWHERE.

31:57.183 --> 32:00.386
WELL, AT 6'6",
HE'S NOT GONNA BE HARD TO MISS.

32:01.187 --> 32:02.989
I HATE YOUR FRIEND.

32:02.989 --> 32:05.657
DEWEY IS AN ACQUIRED TASTE.

32:05.657 --> 32:06.993
WHAT A DICK.

32:06.993 --> 32:09.061
HE'S A HELL OF A COP.

32:09.061 --> 32:11.263
AT LEAST, HE USED TO BE.

32:12.398 --> 32:15.001
YOU KNOW WHAT THEY'RE
CALLING US NOW, RIGHT?

32:15.001 --> 32:16.835
THE WALKING DEAD.

32:16.835 --> 32:18.737
YEAH.

32:18.737 --> 32:19.972
YOU THINK THAT'S FUNNY?

32:19.972 --> 32:20.973
VERY SEXY.

32:20.973 --> 32:22.274
[ CHUCKLES ]

32:22.274 --> 32:24.376
I KIND OF STOPPED CARING
WHAT PEOPLE THINK

32:24.376 --> 32:27.213
AFTER I TOLD MY PARENTS
I WAS GONNA BE A COP.

32:27.213 --> 32:29.815
WHEN DID YOU FIRST KNOW
YOU WANTED TO BE A COP?

32:29.815 --> 32:30.949
[ TIRES SCREECH ]
OH!

32:30.949 --> 32:32.451
AIN'T GOING BACK TO JAIL!

32:32.451 --> 32:35.087
ALL RIGHT. BACK UP.
[ CAR DOORS CLOSE ]

32:35.087 --> 32:37.589
STEP ON OVER THERE, SIR.
[ SCREAMS ]

32:40.692 --> 32:42.628
[ GRUNTING ]

32:47.166 --> 32:49.701
Sammy: RUCKER COULD HAVE GOT
A LOT OF PEOPLE HURT TODAY.

32:49.701 --> 32:51.103
BUT HE DIDN'T.

32:51.103 --> 32:54.173
HE'S PROACTIVE. HE TOOK CHARGE.
HE MADE SHIT HAPPEN.

32:54.173 --> 32:56.042
HE BEAN-BAGGED
AN OLD LADY.

32:56.042 --> 32:58.044
NO, HE BEAN-BAGGED
AN ARMED SUSPECT.

32:58.044 --> 32:59.545
I DIDN'T EVEN SEE
HER SECOND GUN.

32:59.545 --> 33:00.646
SHE'S NOT DEAD.

33:00.646 --> 33:03.582
NONE OF OUR GUYS GOT HURT.
IT'S A GOOD DAY.

33:05.517 --> 33:07.919
[ Chuckling ]
JONES WITH THE NICKNAMES.

33:07.919 --> 33:10.656
NOW SHE'S "GRANBO" FOREVER.

33:11.723 --> 33:14.226
DEPLOYING TASER!

33:14.226 --> 33:16.128
[ TASER CRACKLES ]

33:16.128 --> 33:17.463
THAT ALL YOU GOT?!

33:17.463 --> 33:18.730
[ GRUNTS ]

33:21.333 --> 33:23.402
GOD, HE'S TIGHT.
DOUBLE-CUFF HIM.

33:25.804 --> 33:26.805
THERE WE GO.

33:26.805 --> 33:28.840
YOU ALL RIGHT?

33:28.840 --> 33:30.276
[ GRUNTS ]

33:30.276 --> 33:32.844
PIECE OF SHIT.

33:32.844 --> 33:34.846
[ HIP-HOP MUSIC PLAYING ]

33:34.846 --> 33:36.348
OH.

33:38.850 --> 33:40.652
IT'S A SHAME
TO BREAK THIS UP.

33:49.595 --> 33:51.363
[ MUSIC STOPS,
INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

33:51.363 --> 33:53.232
SORRY, BUT YOU GUYS
HAVE ALL GOT TO GO!

33:53.232 --> 33:54.766
THE OWNER
DOESN'T WANT YOU HERE!

33:54.766 --> 33:57.369
THE OWNER WANTS YOU GONE.
I WANT YOU GONE. LET'S GO.

33:57.369 --> 33:59.305
COME ON. CLEAR OUT.
Sammy:
EVERYBODY OUT. OUT.

33:59.305 --> 34:01.407
LET'S GO.
ARE YOU GONNA
MAKE US GO AWAY?

34:01.407 --> 34:02.841
HEY.
WE AIN'T DOING NOTHING.

34:02.841 --> 34:04.576
GET OUT OF MY FACE.
I'M GONNA HAVE TO ARREST YOU.

34:04.576 --> 34:06.345
LET'S GO.
HEY, HEY, WHOA!

34:06.345 --> 34:07.946
FOR DOING WHAT?
YOU CAN'T PUT YOUR HANDS
ON A COP.

34:07.946 --> 34:10.182
NOW YOUR PARENTS ARE GONNA
HAVE TO BAIL YOU OUT OF JAIL.

34:10.182 --> 34:11.583
Woman:
GET YOUR HANDS OFF OF HER!

34:11.583 --> 34:13.319
GET OFF! NO!
WHOA! WHOA! WHOA!

34:13.319 --> 34:15.287
I'M NOT! COME ON!
LET US JUST DANCE!
Sammy: PARTNER!

34:15.287 --> 34:16.455
GET BACK. GET BACK.

34:16.455 --> 34:18.056
WE AIN'T EVEN
DOING NOTHING.

34:18.056 --> 34:19.057
MISS. MISS.

34:19.057 --> 34:20.259
HEY! WHOA!

34:20.259 --> 34:21.893
WHOA!
YEAH!
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?!

34:21.893 --> 34:23.061
BACK UP!

34:23.061 --> 34:24.062
GET BACK!

34:24.062 --> 34:25.264
[ SPITS, LAUGHS ]

34:25.264 --> 34:27.266
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

34:27.799 --> 34:29.601
GET BACK! GET BACK!

34:29.601 --> 34:30.602
PARTNER!

34:30.602 --> 34:32.138
BACK!

34:32.138 --> 34:34.206
BACK! BACK!

34:34.206 --> 34:36.642
WE WEREN'T
DOING ANYTHING.

34:36.642 --> 34:37.609
HEY. HEY.

34:38.477 --> 34:40.179
EVERYBODY, BACK.
GET HOME. GET HOME.

34:40.179 --> 34:41.713
THIS PARTY IS OVER.

34:45.284 --> 34:46.485
YOU ALL RIGHT?

34:46.485 --> 34:48.154
Ben: YEAH, I'M FINE.
LET'S GO.

34:48.154 --> 34:50.322
COME ON. GET OUT OF MY WAY.
GET THAT --

34:51.790 --> 34:53.892
GET BACK. GET BACK.

34:53.892 --> 34:54.993
HEY.

34:54.993 --> 34:58.597
HEY!
IT'S TIME TO GO HOME! NOW!

34:58.597 --> 35:00.199
OH, YOU WANT TO GET
CUFFED UP NEXT?

35:00.199 --> 35:02.100
GET IN YOUR CARS
AND GET OUT OF HERE!

35:02.100 --> 35:03.402
GET OUT OF HERE!

35:04.403 --> 35:05.604
HE'S SLEEPING
LIKE A BABY.

35:05.604 --> 35:08.774
YEAH, HE KNOWS
WHAT'S ABOUT TO COME.

35:10.842 --> 35:14.246
YOU REALLY WANTED HIM
TO BE INNOCENT, HUH?

35:14.246 --> 35:16.815
MACK LOGAN
COST HIM HIS LIFE. TWICE.

35:16.815 --> 35:19.618
NO, MILLER PUT HIMSELF
BACK IN JAIL.

35:19.618 --> 35:21.920
WHY DO YOU THINK
HE KEPT THE SHOES?

35:21.920 --> 35:23.289
[ SCOFFS ]

35:23.289 --> 35:25.257
IF CRIMINALS WERE SMART,
WE'D BE OUT OF A JOB.

35:25.257 --> 35:26.958
SHOES AND HIS CLOTHES --

35:26.958 --> 35:29.027
ONLY EVIDENCE WE HAVE
OF ANYTHING.

35:29.027 --> 35:33.299
SOMETHING HAPPENS TO THEM,
THIS WHOLE THING DISAPPEARS.

35:33.299 --> 35:36.034
EVIDENCE DISAPPEARS
ALL THE TIME.

35:36.034 --> 35:39.871
IT'S NOT OUR JOB TO FIGURE OUT
WHO WALKS AND WHO DOESN'T.

35:39.871 --> 35:43.342
COME ON. WE MAKE THOSE TYPE
OF JUDGMENT CALLS ALL THE TIME.

35:43.342 --> 35:44.576
[ SIGHS ]

35:44.576 --> 35:46.077
LOOK, A COUPLE THOUSAND
YEARS AGO,

35:46.077 --> 35:47.813
A BUNCH OF GUYS
IN TOGAS DECIDED

35:47.813 --> 35:49.781
NO ONE SHOULD BE
JUDGE AND JURY.

35:49.781 --> 35:52.818
WE COLLECT THE EVIDENCE, AND
THEN WE BRING IT TO SOMEONE ELSE

35:52.818 --> 35:54.920
TO FIGURE OUT
WHAT TO DO WITH IT.

35:54.920 --> 35:56.388
SO YOU THINK
IT WAS RIGHT,

35:56.388 --> 35:58.724
THE WAY WE LIED
TO DARRELL'S GRANDMOTHER?

35:58.724 --> 35:59.725
ABSOLUTELY.

35:59.725 --> 36:00.892
AH. SEE?

36:00.892 --> 36:03.395
YOU -- SEE,
YOU WANT HIM TO BE GUILTY.

36:03.395 --> 36:05.364
I DON'T WANT ANYONE
TO BE GUILTY, RUBEN.

36:05.364 --> 36:07.199
I WANT PEOPLE
TO STOP KILLING EACH OTHER.

36:07.199 --> 36:09.801
BUT WHILE THEY STILL DO,
WE HAVE TO SPEAK FOR THE DEAD

36:09.801 --> 36:11.537
WHETHER THEY DESERVE IT
OR NOT.

36:11.537 --> 36:14.206
DOING THE RIGHT THING
FOR THE WRONG PEOPLE.

36:14.206 --> 36:15.674
SOMETIMES.

36:15.674 --> 36:17.676
LOOK, THE SYSTEM
ISN'T PERFECT,

36:17.676 --> 36:20.746
BUT IT'S THE BEST
ANYONE'S COME UP WITH YET.

36:22.147 --> 36:23.415
[ SIGHS ]

36:23.415 --> 36:26.352
I'M GOING TO GO GET
SOME COFFEE.

36:36.828 --> 36:40.799
WE'RE NOT TALKING
BLACK P. STONES OR ROLLIN' 60s.

36:40.799 --> 36:43.769
WE'RE TALKING
DANCING CATHOLIC-SCHOOL KIDS.

36:45.304 --> 36:47.639
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM, SON?

36:47.639 --> 36:49.641
YOU SCARED
OF BLACK PEOPLE?

36:50.909 --> 36:52.511
NO, SIR.

36:52.511 --> 36:53.579
UH...

36:53.579 --> 36:56.181
[ SIGHS ]
CROWD WAS OUT OF CONTROL.

36:56.181 --> 36:57.883
SITUATION
WAS TURNING HOSTILE.

36:57.883 --> 36:59.818
I LOST CONTACT
WITH MY PARTNER.

36:59.818 --> 37:02.821
ONE OF THE FEMALES IN QUESTION
GRABBED ME,

37:02.821 --> 37:04.923
AND WHEN I WENT
TO SUBDUE HER,

37:04.923 --> 37:07.859
THE OTHER FEMALE,
SHE GOT IN MY FACE.

37:07.859 --> 37:10.462
SHE PUSHED ME.
SHE SLAPPED ME.

37:10.462 --> 37:14.032
AND THEN WHEN SHE SPIT AT ME,
THAT MADE IT AN ASSAULT,

37:14.032 --> 37:16.134
SO THEN...

37:16.134 --> 37:17.636
YOU PUNCHED HER.

37:17.636 --> 37:19.938
CLOSED FIST.

37:19.938 --> 37:21.940
IN THE BEAK.

37:21.940 --> 37:23.409
YES, SIR.

37:23.409 --> 37:26.445
DO YOU HAVE ANYTHING TO ADD,
BRYANT?

37:26.445 --> 37:28.680
SIR, UH,
WE WERE OUTNUMBERED.

37:28.680 --> 37:31.149
OUR TACTICAL ADVANTAGE
WAS COMPROMISED.

37:31.149 --> 37:36.254
OFFICER SHERMAN
MADE A SPLIT-SECOND DECISION.

37:36.254 --> 37:37.589
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:37.589 --> 37:41.126
THIS IS A TOUGH, DIRTY JOB.

37:41.126 --> 37:47.232
THE SYSTEM USED TO GIVE US A LOT
MORE ROPE AND A LOT MORE SOAP.

37:47.232 --> 37:49.368
BUT IT'S A NEW AGE.

37:49.368 --> 37:51.770
A VIDEO AGE.

37:51.770 --> 37:57.376
PEOPLE ARE ALWAYS
WATCHING US.

37:57.376 --> 37:58.844
EVERYWHERE.

38:00.145 --> 38:02.681
ALL RIGHT?

38:03.715 --> 38:04.916
SIR.

38:06.217 --> 38:08.454
ALL RIGHT.

38:15.594 --> 38:18.530
SHERMAN, STEEL YOURSELF.

38:18.530 --> 38:21.533
SOMEBODY OUT THERE
GOT IT ON A CELLPHONE.

38:21.533 --> 38:24.970
YOU'RE ABOUT TO BECOME
"THAT GUY" NOW.

38:26.838 --> 38:28.374
YES, SIR.

38:28.374 --> 38:30.476
CLOSE MY DOOR, PLEASE,
GENTLEMEN.

38:30.476 --> 38:32.611
YES, SIR.
YES, SIR. YES, SIR.

38:34.145 --> 38:35.347
Dewey: HEY, COOP.

38:35.347 --> 38:37.883
WAY TO PUT THE "DON"
IN "DONNYBROOK"

38:37.883 --> 38:39.284
BACK THERE TODAY, MAN.

38:39.284 --> 38:40.386
YOU LOOKED GOOD.

38:40.386 --> 38:42.287
"WALKING DEAD," MY ASS.

38:42.287 --> 38:44.155
HEY, DID YOU HEAR
ABOUT YOUR BOOT?

38:44.155 --> 38:45.657
BUDDY OF MINE
OVER AT ALVARADO

38:45.657 --> 38:47.926
SAYS HE CLOCKED
A 15-YEAR-OLD BLACK CHICK

38:47.926 --> 38:49.094
AT A HIGH-SCHOOL DANCE.

38:49.094 --> 38:50.729
[ LAUGHS ]

38:50.729 --> 38:53.665
STILL STEPPING
ON HIS MEAT, HUH?

38:53.665 --> 38:55.467
I'M PROUD OF HIS ASS!

38:56.468 --> 38:57.669
HEY.
HEY.

38:57.669 --> 38:59.538
YOU GOT A NEW NICKNAME.

38:59.538 --> 39:01.039
YEAH? WHAT'S THAT?

39:01.039 --> 39:04.042
"WU-TANG" 'CAUSE YOU AIN'T
NOTHING TO FUCK WITH.

39:04.042 --> 39:05.744
WHOO! [ LAUGHS ]

39:05.744 --> 39:07.446
HOW'S YOUR BACK?
NEVER BETTER.

39:07.446 --> 39:09.515
MY UNIFORM, ON THE OTHER HAND,
NOT SO GOOD.

39:09.515 --> 39:11.182
OH.
MY GUY'S OUT OF BUSINESS.

39:11.182 --> 39:12.384
WHERE DO YOU GO?
WHAT?

39:12.384 --> 39:13.952
YOU THINK
JUST BECAUSE I'M ASIAN,

39:13.952 --> 39:16.021
I KNOW SOMEONE
WHO DOES ALTERATIONS?

39:16.021 --> 39:17.022
YEAH.

39:17.022 --> 39:18.457
FUCK OFF.

39:18.457 --> 39:20.492
TRY MILT & EDIE'S.

39:20.492 --> 39:22.293
ALL RIGHT.

39:22.293 --> 39:24.129
NIGHT.

39:25.497 --> 39:27.699
[ SIREN WAILS ]

39:28.834 --> 39:30.235
HEY, SHERMAN.

39:30.235 --> 39:31.503
WHAT'S UP?

39:31.503 --> 39:33.371
CAN YOU STOP BY
MY SISTER'S PLACE

39:33.371 --> 39:35.073
AND STRAIGHTEN OUT
MY NIECE?

39:35.073 --> 39:36.007
[ LAUGHS ]

39:36.007 --> 39:37.809
THAT'S FUNNY, MAN.
THAT'S FUNNY.

39:39.044 --> 39:42.514
HEY, UH, THANKS
FOR HAVING MY BACK IN THERE.

39:42.514 --> 39:44.883
YOU ALWAYS
HAVE YOUR PARTNER'S BACK.

39:44.883 --> 39:46.752
ESPECIALLY
WHEN HE'S WRONG.

39:46.752 --> 39:49.154
WERE WE OUTFLANKED?

39:49.154 --> 39:51.222
ABSOLUTELY.

39:51.222 --> 39:52.858
BUT THAT'S THE JOB.

39:52.858 --> 39:55.093
COULDN'T SEE YOU. THINGS WERE
GETTING OUT OF CONTROL.

39:55.093 --> 39:56.027
WELL, YOU...

39:56.027 --> 39:58.129
YOU KIND OF
LOST YOUR COOL.

39:58.129 --> 39:59.330
YOU -- YOU GOT TO...

39:59.330 --> 40:01.567
YOU GOT TO TRY
NOT TO LOSE YOUR COOL.

40:01.567 --> 40:04.970
THE ONLY THING THAT MAKES US
DIFFERENT FROM THEM

40:04.970 --> 40:07.005
IS THAT EVEN WHEN THEY'RE
FIRING AT US,

40:07.005 --> 40:08.940
WE DON'T FIRE BACK
BECAUSE WE'RE MAD.

40:08.940 --> 40:10.742
WE FIRE BACK
TO SAVE LIVES.

40:12.978 --> 40:14.112
YOU'RE RIGHT.

40:14.112 --> 40:15.413
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

40:15.413 --> 40:17.148
YEAH.
LONG DRIVE.

40:23.121 --> 40:24.422
Anawalt: HEY.

40:25.457 --> 40:27.626
NICE WORK OUT THERE.

40:27.626 --> 40:29.094
THANK YOU.

40:29.094 --> 40:31.262
OH, AND...

40:31.262 --> 40:33.865
YOU DROPPED THIS.

40:45.877 --> 40:47.913
[ SIGHS ]
